column13: We are from REACH, an NGO that does assessments to understand needs of people in the community. We share our results with humanitarian organizations so they can better plan and organize their responses. Today, we randomly selected your household to do an assessment. You will not receive anything for participating, and if you choose not to participate it will not affect your ability to receive humanitarian services. The interview will take about 30 minutes. Do you agree to participate?
